00:09:39.560 --> 00:09:45.130
FIRST IN HER CLASS AS AN UNDERGRADUATE AT
CORNELL AND FIRST IN HER CLASS AT COLUMBIA

00:09:45.130 --> 00:09:46.470
LAW SCHOOL.

00:09:46.470 --> 00:09:53.230
TALK ABOUT A GO GETTER.

