00:09:55.210 --> 00:10:00.250
AND JUSTICE GINSBURG IN HER COLLEGE YEARS
WAS MORE THAN STUDIOUS.

00:10:00.250 --> 00:10:05.360
AT CORNELL SHE BECAME FAST FRIENDS WITH THE
OTHER WOMEN ON HER FLOOR.

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:11.970
THEY CALLED THEMSELVES KHLABIJ, AN ACRONYM
OF THEIR FIRST NAMES, STARTING WITH KICKY

00:10:11.970 --> 00:10:12.980
AS THE "K."

00:10:12.980 --> 00:10:19.900
THAT GROUP OF FRIENDS, SIX OF THEM NOW, HAVE
GOTTEN TOGETHER AS RECENTLY AS LAST YEAR.

00:10:19.900 --> 00:10:27.840
WHILE NOT EVERYONE HAS AN ACRONYM FOR THEIR
ROOMMATES, THE TENT TODAY IS FILLED WITH PEOPLE

00:10:27.840 --> 00:10:33.590
WHO STARTED FRIENDSHIPS IN COLLEGE HALLWAYS,
AND WHO CONTINUE TO STAY CONNECTED AND TO

00:10:33.590 --> 00:10:35.520
BE IMPORTANT FOR ONE ANOTHER.

00:10:35.520 --> 00:10:43.380
FOR THE WOMEN OF KHLABIJ, IT WOULD HAVE BEEN
IMPOSSIBLE TO PREDICT OUR WORLD IN WHICH THREE

00:10:43.380 --> 00:10:48.480
WOMEN SERVE ON THE SUPREME COURT, A WOMAN
IS THE PRESIDENT OF HARVARD HARVARD HARVARD

00:10:48.480 --> 00:10:56.770
UNIVERSITY, THE CEOS OF GENERAL MOTORS, IBM,
AND PEPSICO ARE WOMEN. A FEMALE FORMER SECRETARY

00:10:56.770 --> 00:10:59.440
OF STATE IS RUNNING FOR PRESIDENT.

00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:05.380
THE U.S. ARMED FORCES INCLUDES FOUR WOMEN
