01:07:16.630 --> 01:07:23.490
WE HAVE SEEN TODAY THAT YOU CAN ASK QUESTIONS
AS IMPRESSIVELY AS YOU CAN ANSWER THEM.

01:07:23.490 --> 01:07:25.359
AND WE ARE VERY GRATEFUL TO YOU FOR BOTH.

01:07:25.359 --> 01:07:28.459
SO THANK YOU.

01:07:28.459 --> 01:07:30.969
[APPLAUSE]

01:07:30.969 --> 01:07:40.039
AND OF COURSE TO JUSTICE GINSBURG, THANK YOU
FOR GIVING US SUCH A MARVELOUS DAY.

01:07:40.039 --> 01:07:45.799
YOU SO GENEROUSLY SHARED YOUR TIME, YOUR INSIGHTS,
