01:07:51.920 --> 01:07:54.999
HERE IS THE CITATION.

01:07:54.999 --> 01:08:03.650
SHE IS A PASSIONATE ADVOCATE FOR EQUALITY
AND A DISPASSIONATE JURIST FOR JUSTICE.

01:08:03.650 --> 01:08:10.829
WHETHER IN THE MAJORITY OR THE MINORITY, SHE
ILLUMINATES A PATH TOWARD A SOCIETY OF GREATER

01:08:10.829 --> 01:08:13.589
FAIRNESS AND DIGNITY.

01:08:13.589 --> 01:08:21.460
SHE ELEVATES THE WORK OF THE COURT BY RESPECTING
HER OPPONENTS WHILE HOLDING STEADFAST TO HER

